### Changed (2026-06-03 menu/release)

- Restored mobile navigation behavior by reintroducing the Menu toggle button on all public pages.
- Re-enabled small-screen dropdown menu styling and open/close behavior so Home, Ethics, and Code of Conduct links are accessible on mobile.
- Verified release publication for tag v20260603 on both GitHub and Codeberg.
- Prepared release automation guidance for Codeberg and validated release endpoint behavior for the project repository.

### Files (2026-06-03 menu/release)

