- index.html
- ethics.html
- coc.html
- styles.css

### Changed (2026-06-03 mobile alignment)

- Fixed small-screen header alignment so the QB Networks brand block (logo + Home link target) stays centered.
- Moved the navigation directly under the centered brand block on mobile by showing the menu list inline in the header stack.
- Removed the mobile Menu toggle button for this layout so users always see Home, Ethics, and Code of Conduct links below the brand.

### Files (2026-06-03 mobile alignment)

- ChangeLog
- styles.css

### Changed (2026-06-03 menu/style + release script)

- Updated header navigation styling so Home, Ethics, and Code of Conduct links sit directly below the centered QB Networks brand in a horizontal row on small screens.
- Matched desktop brand presentation to the same centered stacked look used on mobile for consistent top navigation layout.
- Kept the existing QB Networks logo artwork while removing temporary white-background styling in the SVG so the original logo remains unchanged and transparent.
- Added a reusable release automation script to create GitHub and Codeberg releases with interactive token prompts and API error handling.

